--- Part 3: Summary ---
  CONFIRMED: beta_1(T\v) = 0 for ALL vertices of beta_3=1 tournaments!
  This is STRONGER than the seesaw (which only says b1*b3=0 per tournament)
  It says: if b3(T)=1, then ALL deletions have b1=0
  This forces H_2(T,T\v) = 0 for ALL vertices (from LES)
  Combined with H_0^rel = 0, H_1^rel = 0, the relative complex simplifies to:
    H_p^rel = 0 for p != 3, and H_3^rel in {0,1}

DONE.
